ALCON: Note changes in 2nd RGMT participation in the Mapping mission.

Chief Roach - good work: in the COMMs plan please list who will have Net co=
ntrol on each day of the exercise if that is relevant to the exercise. Let=
=92s stress HF throughout so that we get in some good repetitions.

SGM Nunley - this can be in the next FRAGO. Get back to MAJ Wemyss and chie=
f Roach as needed for details.

Request of the COMMs plan is now w/Chief Roach of 2nd RGMT, so 3rd does not=
 need to put in the request.

Standby for more info as it comes our way.

V/R

LTC Estes

